.................... ////     Call to write a 64 bit integer                                     //// 
.................... ////                                                                        //// 
.................... ////   int64 read_int64_eeprom(address)                                     //// 
.................... ////     Call to read a 64 bit integer                                      //// 
.................... ////                                                                        //// 
